<p><a name="Relationship_with_existentialism_and_nihilism" id="Relationship_with_existentialism_and_nihilism"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Absurdism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Relationship with existentialism and nihilism">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Relationship with existentialism and nihilism</span></h2>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
<td>
<table>
